ArcoLinux Spices Application

This application will assist you in getting the ArcoLinux packages from the ArcoLinux repositories.

It will install the latest ArcoLinux .bashrc and replace yours with it.

It will install all packages we use in the .bashrc.

It will import the ArcoLinux signing key.

It can fix issues with server connections hosting the keys.

Download the package and install it with this command

sudo pacman -U packagename

Youtube tutorial

https://arcolinux.info/download/arcolinux-spices-application/

